description: Power Line has discovered Henry Clerk's plan to explode every nuclear reactor in the United States, releasing massive radiation. Now they have to find St. George, to enlist the aid of Dr. Zero. Unfortunately, the Abbott of the Order of St. George has taken up the armor to destroy Zero. Meanwhile, Michael Devlin continues to 'hang out' in Venezuela.
name: The Mouth Of Truth

description: The showdown between St. George and Schreck...but St. George doesn't have his armor! Meanwhile, Henry Clerk kills Dr. Zero's lover, but Zero thinks the Order of St. George is guilty. He'll exact swift and brutal revenge. Plus, a peek into Clerk's college days...Serial Killer 101.
name: The Crossing of the Return Threshold

description: Our hero is injured and unable to wear the armor and battle. Father Abbot, the man who made the armor with his own powers, decides to wear it himself and continue the fight. This does not sit well with some of his colleagues, whose disagreements come to mild physical violence.
